{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be professional and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Smart Home Innovations</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2a4d69;\n            --secondary-color: #4b86a1;\n            --accent-color: #8ab6d6;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #f0f4f8;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section:nth-of-type(even) {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 30%;\n            margin: 20px 1.5%;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            vertical-align: top;\n        }\n\n        .feature:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .feature i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .feature h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .feature p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n   